  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nVersion: 1.10.22-unstable\r\nGit Commit: c4ab7d229117fdaa24292d84c1d450a727cb3e9f\r\nArchitecture: amd64\r\nGo Version: go1.18.5\r\nOperating System: linux\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nAfter calling JSON-RPC method `personal_signTransaction` with `maxFeePerGas` **or** `maxPriorityFeePerGas` I expect to get signed transaction:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"result\": {\r\n        \"raw\": \"...\",\r\n        \"tx\": {\r\n            \"type\": \"0x2\",\r\n            \"nonce\": \"0x00\",\r\n            \"gasPrice\": null,\r\n            \"maxPriorityFeePerGas\": \"0x3b9aca00\",\r\n            \"maxFeePerGas\": \"0x3b9aca00\",\r\n            \"gas\": \"0x5208\",\r\n            \"value\": \"0x3a98\",\r\n            \"input\": \"0x\",\r\n            \"v\": \"0x1\",\r\n            \"r\": \"...\",\r\n            \"s\": \"...\",\r\n            \"to\": \"...\",\r\n            \"chainId\": \"0x3039\",\r\n            \"accessList\": [],\r\n            \"hash\": \"...\"\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nInstead I get error about missing gasPrice/maxFeePerGas/maxPriorityFeePerGas. If I specify **both** `maxFeePerGas` and `maxPriorityFeePerGas` I would get correct response with signed transaction.\r\n```\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"error\":{\"code\":-32000,\"message\":\"missing gasPrice or maxFeePerGas/maxPriorityFeePerGas\"}}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n```\r\ncurl --location --request POST 'http://127.0.0.1:8545' \\\r\n--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\r\n--data-raw '{ \r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\", \r\n    \"method\": \"personal_signTransaction\", \r\n    \"params\": [{ \r\n        \"from\": \"<from address>\", \r\n        \"to\": \"<to address>\", \r\n        \"gas\": \"0x5208\", \r\n        \"value\": \"0x3a98\",\r\n        \"maxFeePerGas\": \"0x3b9aca00\",\r\n        \"nonce\": \"0x00\" \r\n        }, \"password\"\r\n    ], \r\n    \"id\": 1 \r\n}'\r\n```\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/948e08d55bf185e4b80ca7a10d689cbfd3f7fcdd/internal/ethapi/api.go#L484\r\nThis line expects `gasPrice` or `maxFeePerGas` + `maxPriorityFeePerGas`. As far as I know `maxFeePerGas` or `maxPriorityFeePerGas` only is enough, isn't it?",
